      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MCCLUGGAGE (5) goes very well at the course with three wins and a placing from five starts. Scored by 0.8 lengths last time (25.45) in a Restricted WIN over 457m at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. TWO FACED GWEN (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (20.52) at Capalaba behind Jill's Juliette in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Leading player again. FEDERAL SAKI (3) hit the frame last time at Rockhampton but the start prior rocketed around 407m at Rockhampton in 23.60. Has the ability and looks a key chance. FLYING MCKEON (2) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
